ink><description>据中国地震台网中心周一消息，中国四川省木里县发生5.0级地震。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:37:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/earthquake-magnitude-50-hits-chinas-sichuan-province-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>在中国，星巴克试图避免价格战却陷入打折潮</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-starbucks-tries-avoid-price-war-gets-dragged-into-discounting-2024-05-27/</link><description>由于星巴克在中国的啤酒业务面临着来自快速增长、低成本竞争对手的激烈竞争，这些竞争对手已经蚕食了星巴克的市场份额，这家咖啡连锁店正越来越多地被拖入其声称希望避免的价格战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:33:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-starbucks-tries-avoid-price-war-gets-dragged-into-discounting-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-05-27/</link><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:30:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国设立第三只基金 475 亿美元提振半导体行业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-sets-up-475-bln-state-fund-boost-semiconductor-industry-2024-05-27/</link><description>根据向政府运营的公司注册处提交的文件，中国已计划设立第三个国家支持投资基金，以促进半导体行业发展，注册资本为 3440 亿元人民币（475 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 03:11:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-sets-up-475-bln-state-fund-boost-semiconductor-industry-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国“资产荒”抑制央行债券交易雄心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/asset-famine-china-curbs-central-banks-bond-trading-ambitions-2024-05-27/</link><description>中国金融部门低风险资产的稀缺正在阻碍央行在中断17年后重返国债市场以提高其货币政策工具箱效率的计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 02:55:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/asset-famine-china-curbs-central-banks-bond-trading-ambitions-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>发言人称日本要求朝鲜取消卫星火箭发射</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-demands-north-korea-cancel-satellite-rocket-launch-spokesperson-says-2024-05-27/</link><description>日本政府最高发言人、内阁官房长官林芳正周一表示，东京已通过北京的外交渠道要求朝鲜取消计划的卫星火箭发射。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 02:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-demands-north-korea-cancel-satellite-rocket-launch-spokesperson-says-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国房地产开发商佳兆业清算听证会延期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-court-adjourns-liquidation-hearing-china-developer-kaisa-2024-05-27/</link><description>周一，香港一家法院将寻求佳兆业集团清算的请愿书的听证会推迟至 6 月 24 日，这让这家陷入困境的中国开发商在实施债务重组计划时得到了一些喘息的机会。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 02:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-court-adjourns-liquidation-hearing-china-developer-kaisa-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>1-4月全国规模以上工业利润增长4.3%，与一季度持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-profits-rise-43-jan-april-unchanged-q1-2024-05-27/</link><description>周一官方数据显示，今年前四个月中国工业企业利润同比增长4.3%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 01:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-profits-rise-43-jan-april-unchanged-q1-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>全球通胀数据公布前美元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-ahead-global-inflation-data-2024-05-27/</link><description>周一，美元本周开局稳定，投资者关注美国、欧洲和日本通胀数据，以指导全球利率前景。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 01:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-ahead-global-inflation-data-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着美国和欧盟通胀数据的临近，亚洲股​​市小幅走高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-27/</link><description>亚洲股市周一坚挺，因投资者准备迎接一系列繁忙的通胀数据，这些数据可能为欧洲最早下周降息以及美国在短短几个月内放松政策奠定基础。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 00:25:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国总理欢呼与美国盟友韩国、日本的“新开始”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-premier-hold-rare-summit-with-us-allied-south-korea-japan-2024-05-26/</link><description>四年来的首次三方会谈旨在恢复因全球紧张局势而受阻的贸易和安全对话。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 22:33:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-premier-hold-rare-summit-with-us-allied-south-korea-japan-2024-05-26/</guid></item><item><title>官员称巴基斯坦逮捕了11名参与杀害中国工程师的武装分子</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-arrests-11-militants-involved-chinese-engineers-killing-say-officials-2024-05-26/</link><description>官员周日表示，巴基斯坦当局逮捕了 11 名伊斯兰激进分子，他们参与了 3 月份在该国北部与阿富汗接壤的自杀式爆炸事件，导致 5 名中国工程师死亡。</description><pubDate>Sun, 26 May 2024 14:34:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-arrests-11-militants-involved-chinese-engineers-killing-say-officials-2024-05-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>